      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok i think i follow. so the rebar is basically just hidden inside the concrete to catch those tension forces. but what happens if something goes wrong inside the concrete? like if there are gaps or if the bond between the steel and the concrete is bad... does that cause any specific kinds of damage to the foundation?",
